com.android.network

Class TicTacToeGameAPIImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.network.TicTacToeGameAPIImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TicTacToeGameAPI

    public class TicTacToeGameAPIImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements TicTacToeGameAPI
    TicTacToeGameAPIImpl is an implementation of TicTacToeGameAPI interface to handle Client - Game Server networking functions of TicTacToe game. It encapsulates the thread-based network functions into a simple function.
    Author:
    davidsoendoro-rohitgoyal
